json_ld.name: Dry Dog Food
json_ld.description: Discover our premium selection of dry dog food at great prices, tailored to nourish every dog based on age, size, breed or special health needs. Our extensive range includes dry kibbles, grain-free dry dog food, single protein kibble options and much more, recognising that each dog has unique dietary requirements. Alternatively, consider our wet dog food, canned dog food and convenient pouches.

item.name: Skinner’s Field & Trial Adult Salmon & Rice Dry Dog Food
item.description: A hypoallergenic dry dog food with salmon and rice, free from gluten, wheat, maize, barley, soya and milk products, with a combination of rice, oats, peas and salmon from sustainable sources.

item.name: Skinner’s Field & Trial Adult Maintenance Chicken Dry Dog Food
